FT  19 FEB 93 / Letter: A better beer
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   From Mr CHRISTOPH ULL
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Sir, With regard to your promotion 'Enjoy Club Europe: two for the price of
one - Vienna', I make this comment. The saying Gut, Besser, Goesser is not a
typical saying of the Viennese. Goesser is a Styrian beer and Gut, Besser,
Goesser is a slogan of the Steirerbraeu AG, a Styrian company, which
produces and promotes Goesser Bier. As a Styrian I would like to invite you
to Austria and taste the difference between the Styrian beer and the beer
produced near Vienna - you will stay in Styria forever.
Christoph Ull,
Emannuel College,
Cambridge CB2 3AP
